cs.SI, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.HC, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on predicting the popularity of social media posts and understanding the factors that influence their popularity.
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of point process-based models to predict the future trend in the popularity of social media posts.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper proposes a model that incorporates visual reasoning to improve prediction accuracy.
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is a possible category as the paper discusses how the proposed system supports users to uncover the working mechanism behind the model and improve the prediction accuracy based on the insights gained.
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper mentions the use of realistic WeChat articles to demonstrate the effectiveness of the system.
